<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbe518e7e-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s7574"><num value="7574">§ 7574.</num><heading> Definitions</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Terms used in this part (other than Administrator) shall have the same meaning as such terms have under <ref href="/us/usc/t49/s40102/a">section 40102(a) of title 49</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbe518e7f-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/act/1955-07-14/ch360">July 14, 1955, ch. 360</ref>, title II, § 234, as added <ref href="/us/pl/91/604/s11/a/1">Pub. L. 91–604, § 11(a)(1)</ref>, <date date="1970-12-31">Dec. 31, 1970</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/84/1705">84 Stat. 1705</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idbe518e80-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idbe518e81-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="idbe518e82-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">In text, “<ref href="/us/usc/t49/s40102/a">section 40102(a) of title 49</ref>” substituted for “section 101 of the Federal Aviation Act of 1958” on authority of <ref href="/us/pl/103/272/s6/b">Pub. L. 103–272, § 6(b)</ref>, <date date="1994-07-05">July 5, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/1378">108 Stat. 1378</ref>, the first section of which enacted subtitles II, III, and V to X of Title 49, Transportation.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was formerly classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s1857f–12">section 1857f–12 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
